# Pinned jar bill-of-materials for the Spark Connect + Iceberg EKS image (Tier A).
# Format: `sha1sum -c` compatible (sha1<two spaces>basename). Checksums are the
# canonical `.sha1` published alongside each artifact on Maven Central.
#
# These pins are the reproducibility contract: fetch-jars.sh downloads each
# artifact and verifies it against this file. A 4.1->4.2/5.0 bump = update the
# versions in build.sh AND replace the lines below with the new basenames+sha1s.
#
# Tier B (5.0-SNAPSHOT + iceberg-port base) bakes the Iceberg runtime INTO the
# base image, so fetch-jars.sh drops the iceberg line when ICEBERG_IN_BASE=true.
